Authentique basic polyvalent du dressing Femme, ce pantalon ajusté en cady s’adaptera à toutes les occasions en fonction de la nature des looks. Ce modèle non doublé présente une coupe classique et élégante. Fermeture latérale zippée. Longueur : 95 cm

description: These classic silk cady sweatpants combine chic style with practicality: the slim cut is flattering, while the ankle zip detail ensures maximum comfort. Rounded pockets in front and side zip fastening. Leg cuff width 15.5 cm / 6.1 in. Made in Italy.
name: CLASSIC SILK CADY SWEATPANTS

description: With its classic design and original composition, this pure wool jacket is perfect for adding a personal touch to an outfit.   The piece features a refined Ottoman construction which emphasises the fitted, feminine silhouette.    The garment contains pointed lapels, padded shoulders covered in satin, patch pockets and single-breasted fastening with one covered button.  Length 64 cm / 25.2 in. Made in Italy.
name: SINGLE-BREASTED WOOL JACKET

description: Elegant yet not too formal. This two-toned matching silk cady jacket has notched lapels, padded shoulders, long wrist-length sleeves, side bands which emphasize the waist and a seam pocket on the rounded side.  Single-breasted fastening with special press studs. Length 68 cm / 27 in. Made in Italy.
name: SINGLE-BREASTED SILK CADY JACKET

description: This stretch double wool jacket, soft to the touch and slim-fitting, stands out for its innovative, figure-flattering design. This model has shawl lapels, double welted pockets, a rounded edge and high cuffs finished in ribbed knit.   Single-breasted fastening with press studs. Length: 64 cm / 25 in. Made in Italy.
name: DOUBLE WOOL JACKET

description: Bold lines and refined details make this silk cady jacket an authentic reflection of contemporary femininity. The piece has been meticulously constructed to highlight the body, with a crew neck collar, padded shoulders and seam pockets.  Single-breasted double zip fastening. Length: 62 cm / 24.4 in. Made in Italy.
name: SINGLE-BREASTED SILK CADY JACKET
